{"title_page": "Snooker world rankings 1982/1983", "text_new": "{{Blacklisted-links|1=\n*http://www.cuetracker.net/pages/rankings.php?list=1982/1983&sort=start\n*:''Triggered by <code>\\bcuetracker\\.net\\b</code> on the local blacklist''|bot=Cyberbot II|invisible=false}}\n'''Snooker world rankings 1982/1983''': The professional [[snooker world rankings|world rankings]] for the top 33 [[snooker]] players in the [[1982\u201383 snooker season|1982\u201383 season]] are listed below.\n\n{{Infobox snooker player\n| name          = No. 1: [[Ray Reardon]]\n| image         = \n| birth_date    = {{birth date and age|1932|10|8}}\n| Sport country = {{WAL}}\n| Professional  = 1967\u20131992\n| High ranking  = 1\n}}\n\n{{Infobox snooker player\n| name          = No. 2: [[Alex Higgins]]\n| image         = Alex Higgins.jpg\n| birth_date    = {{Birth date|1949|3|18|df=y}}\n| death_date    = {{Death date and age|2010|7|24|1949|3|18|df=y}}\n| Sport country = <!--USE OF FLAGICONS FOR NIR STRONGLY DEPRECATED.-->[[Northern Ireland]]\n| Professional  = 1971\u20131997\n| High ranking  = 2\n}}\n\n{{Infobox snooker player\n| name          = No. 3: [[Cliff Thorburn]]\n| image         = Cliff Thorburn.jpg\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1948|1|16}}\n| Sport country = {{CAN}}\n| Professional  = 1972\u20131996\n| High ranking  = 1\n}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! No.<ref>{{cite web|last=Turner|first=Chris|title=Historical World Rankings 1975/76 to 1989/90|url=http://www.cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/HistoricRank1.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120608214119/http://www.cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/HistoricRank1.html|archivedate=8 June 2012|work=cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk|publisher=Chris Turner's Snooker Archive|accessdate=26 February 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ranking History|url=http://www.snooker.org/rnk/history.asp?sort=1982/1983&order=asc|publisher=Snooker.org|accessdate=6 February 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Hayton|first=Eric|title=The CueSport Book of Profession