ME''' ||colspan=7| '''May 19 - Lyceum Gym'''\n|- bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n| '''Team''' || ''1st'' || ''2nd'' || ''3rd'' || ''4th'' || ''5th'' || ''Best Player''\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 3 PM || [[Lyceum of the Philippines University|Lyceum Lady Pirates]] || 16 || 19 || 17 || - || - ||rowspan=2| Mary Jean Balse of UST\n|-\n| '''[[University of Santo Tomas|UST Lady Tigers]]''' || '''25''' || '''25''' || '''25''' || - || -\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 5 PM || [[Far Eastern University|FEU Lady Tamaraws]] || 21 || 20 || 20 || - || - ||rowspan=2| Maureen Penetrante of La Salle\n|-\n| '''[[De La Salle University-Manila|La Salle Lady Archers]]''' || '''25''' || '''25''' || '''25''' || - || -\n|-\n|- bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n|rowspan=2| '''TIME''' ||colspan=7| '''May 21 - Rizal Memorial Coliseum'''\n|- bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n| '''Team''' || ''1st'' || ''2nd'' || ''3rd'' || ''4th'' || ''5th'' || ''Best Player''\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 3 PM || '''[[De La Salle University-Manila|La Salle Lady Archers]]''' || '''25''' || '''25''' || '''25''' || - || - ||rowspan=2| Maureen Penetrante of La Salle\n|-\n| [[Lyceum of the Philippines University|Lyceum Lady Pirates]] || 16 || 20 || 23 || - || -\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 5 PM || [[University of Santo Tomas|UST Lady Tigers]] || '''25''' || 22 || 17 || '''25''' || 11 ||rowspan=2| Patricia Lynn Taganas of Ateneo\n|-\n| '''[[Ateneo de Manila University|Ateneo Lady Eagles]]''' || 21 || '''25''' || '''25''' || 19 || '''15'''\n|-\n|- bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n|rowspan=2| '''TIME''' ||colspan=7| '''May 23 - Rizal Memorial Coliseum'''\n|- bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n| '''Team''' || ''1st'' || ''2nd'' || ''3rd'' || ''4th'' || ''5th'' || ''Best Player''\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 3 PM || [[Far Eastern University|FEU Lady Tamaraws]] || 19 || 14 || 12 || - || - ||rowspan=2| Roxanne Pimentel of UST\n|-\n| [[University of Santo Tomas|UST Lady Tigers]] || '''25''' || '''25''' || '''25''' || - || -\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 5 PM || [[Lyceum of the Philippines University|Lyceum Lady Pirates]] || 20 || 18 || 21 || - || - ||rowspa